WORKS | E | log2(p(n)) pi(x) calls, each O(x^{2/3}) | 5 |\n97\t| Recursive pi(x) via pi(x/2) | FAIL | I | Error O(sqrt(x)/ln^2(x)), too large | 7 |\n98\t| Recursive identity (8 methods) | FAIL | E | All reduce to Meissel-Lehmer or explicit formula | 9 |\n99\t| GCD/coprimality matrix | FAIL | I | Eigenvalues != primes | 8 |\n100\t| Newton's identities (power sums) | WORKS | E | O(x^{2/3}) per sum, unstable deg>50 | 7 |"}]},"uuid":"bf93a364-3301-401a-8e21-98599db5b932","timestamp":"2026-04-04T18:37:54.967Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"71bd5c53-6b9d-4f6c-bc0b-bf8004dec9d1","userType":"external","entrypoint":"sdk-cli","cwd":"/apps/aplikacijos/prime-research","sessionId":"f8730f89-3e52-4285-b6af-b645d01a4c7f","version":"2.1.92","gitBranch":"main","slug":"tranquil-yawning-sparkle"}
